<p><strong>Distances from the Sheraton Gateway Hotel Los Angeles</strong></p>
<blockquote dir="ltr" style="margin-right: 0px;">
<p><strong>To/From Airports:</strong><br />Los Angeles Intl Airport -- .5 MI (5 min) <br /><em>The Sheraton Gateway offers free&nbsp;shuttle transportation to/from LAX</em></p>
<p>Long Beach Municipal Airport -- 15 MI (25 min)</p>
<p>Bob Hope Airport (Burbank) -- 28 MI (34 min)</p>
<p>John Wayne Airport&nbsp; (Orange County) -- 40 MI (40 min)</p>
<p>Ontario International Airport -- 54 MI (55 min)</p>
<p><strong>To/From Amtrak Station</strong> <br />Downtown Los Angeles-Union Station -- 14 MI</p>
</blockquote>
<p dir="ltr"><strong>Driving directions to the Sheraton Gateway Hotel Los Angeles</strong></p>
<blockquote dir="ltr" style="margin-right: 0px;">
<p dir="ltr"><strong>Driving directions from LAX Airport:</strong> <input width="343" height="221" align="right" type="image" src="http://isdc.nss.org/isdc/2006/Sheraton map.gif" longdesc="undefined" /><br />Exit the airport via Century Boulevard, to the first stop light which is Avion Street, hotel is on the left. <br /><br /><strong>From the North:</strong><br />Take Interstate 405 South and exit at Century Boulevard West (LAX Airport). Turn left at the bottom of the off ramp, and turn right on Century. The hotel is located on the right side of Century Boulevard. Turn right on Avion and take an immediate left to the hotel. <br /><br /><strong>From the South:<br /></strong>Take I-405 North and exit at Century Boulevard. Turn left at the light and travel west on Century Boulevard. The hotel is located on the right side of Century Boulevard. Turn right at Avion and then immediately to the hotel. <br /><br /><strong>From the East:<br /></strong>Take Interstate 10 West to I-405 South and exit at Century Boul e    vard West. Turn left at the bottom of the off ramp and take a right on Century. The hotel is located on the right side of Century Boulev ard. Turn right on Avion and take an immediate left to the hotel.</p>
<p dir="ltr"><strong>From the West:<br /></strong>Swim hard. Dodge </p>
</blockquote>
<p align="left" dir="ltr"><a name="american"></a><strong>American Airlines&nbsp;Discount</strong></p>
<blockquote dir="ltr" style="margin-right: 0px;">
<h5 class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><a href="http://www.aa.com">American Airlines</a> offering 5% discount to ISDC. Enter code A4956AT in the AA.com discount code box. (NOTE: You must fly in and out of LAX between May 1-11 and if your booking code is either a Q or O you will NOT receive the discount.) Other restrictions may apply. </h5>
